origination.label: Creator
origination.corpname: City University of New York. City College

accessrestrict.head: Conditions Governing Access
accessrestrict.p: Open for research. Brittle or damaged items are available at the discretion of RAC.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: Collection consists of reports, studies, field reports, conference and workshop papers, annual reports, yearbooks, financial statements, and budgets collected by the Russell Sage Foundation library.

acqinfo.head: Immediate Source of Acquisition
acqinfo.p: Donated to RAC as an unrestricted gift by City College of New York in 2018.

custodhist.head: Custodial History
custodhist.p: The contents of this collection was originally transferred to the City College of New York directly from Russell Sage Foundation. RAC then received the holdings from CCNY.
